<!DOCTYPE html>
<html lang="en">
<head>
    <meta charset="UTF-8">
    <meta name="viewport" content="width=device-width, initial-scale=1.0">
    <title><%= title %></title>
    <style>
        body { 
            font-family: Arial, sans-serif; 
            margin: 0; 
            padding: 0; 
            background: linear-gradient(135deg, #f06, #4a90e2); 
            color: #fff;
        }
        .hero { padding: 50px 20px; text-align: center; }
        .hero h1 { font-size: 3em; margin: 0; }
        .hero p { font-size: 1.2em; }
        .cta { margin-top: 20px; }
        .cta button { padding: 10px 20px; font-size: 1em; }
        .features, .how-it-works, .testimonials, .footer { padding: 50px 20px; text-align: center; }
        .features h2, .how-it-works h2, .testimonials h2 { font-size: 2em; margin-bottom: 20px; }
        .footer { background: #333; color: #fff; }
    </style>
</head>
<body>
    <div class="hero">
        <h1>Welcome to PolyFusion</h1>
        <p>Create and explore 2D and 3D shapes with ease.</p>
        <div class="cta">
            <button>Get Started</button>
        </div>
    </div>
    <div class="features">
        <h2>Features</h2>
        <p>Explore our powerful shape-building tools and detailed shape information.</p>
    </div>
    <div class="how-it-works">
        <h2>How It Works</h2>
        <p>Follow these simple steps to get started with Shape Builder.</p>
    </div>
    <div class="testimonials">
        <h2>Testimonials</h2>
        <p>See what our users are saying about Shape Builder.</p>
    </div>
    <div class="footer">
        <p>Made by: </p>
        <p>Follow us on social media</p>
    </div>
</body>
</html>
